  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="question-text">
      Refer to the exhibit. What three facts can be determined from the viewable output of the show ip interface brief command? (Choose three.)
    </p>
    <div class="options" id="opts-71">
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="0">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">A</span>
        <span class="opt-text">Two devices are attached to the switch.</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="1">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">B</span>
        <span class="opt-text">The default SVI has been configured.</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="2">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">C</span>
        <span class="opt-text">The switch can be remotely managed.</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="3">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">D</span>
        <span class="opt-text">Two physical interfaces have been configured.</span>
